<signature>
BakeMesh(Mesh)
</signature>
Creates a snapshot of SkinnedMeshRenderer and stores it in /mesh/.
The vertices are relative to the SkinnedMeshRenderer Transform component. Note that the snapshot is still computed even when ::ref::updateWhenOffscreen is set to false and the skinned mesh object is currently offscreen.
@param mesh A static mesh that will receive the snapshot of the skinned mesh.